    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爱与希望的故事</h2><i>“你或许愿意为爱人走到世界尽头，但你愿意跨越尽头，踏入未知之域吗？”</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/29ef9d839218f167be98d0f1d8871f4d.poster.avif?t=1667488910\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/29ef9d839218f167be98d0f1d8871f4d.webm?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/29ef9d839218f167be98d0f1d8871f4d.mp4?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《Eternal Hope》中，你将进入提比的故事，这个可爱的男孩失去了一生所爱。你将和他一同踏上极不寻常的旅程，为了将他心爱女友的灵魂从炼狱般的暗影世界带回来。但这个新世界之旅并非易事。一路前进的过程中，你需要克服艰难险阻，解开疑难谜团。<br><br>提比从灵魂守护者那得到空间转换能力后，可以遨游四方，解决谜题，并遇见生活在暗影之中的超凡生灵。在这段旅程中，与提比一起穿越世界尽头，并揭开凡人不得而知的古老秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/80c40caab0be19aabcba098548a3ed8a.poster.avif?t=1667488910\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/80c40caab0be19aabcba098548a3ed8a.webm?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/80c40caab0be19aabcba098548a3ed8a.mp4?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Eternal Hope》特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>踏上通往黑暗神奇世界的旅程，这里充满未解之谜！<br></li><li>穿越神秘森林、隐藏洞穴、古老城市，一路上山，来到灵魂圣殿。<br></li><li>使用特殊力量在不同的世界之间转换，改变游戏环境。<br></li><li>借助帮忙，解决谜题！使用暗影世界的环境和生物来克服眼前的障碍。<br></li><li>朋友还是敌人？遇见独特的生物，进一步了解居住在暗影世界的物种的一切。<br></li><li>美妙的原创配乐，让你沉浸在提比动人的故事之中。<br></li><li>穿越回忆如画的场景，体验独一无二的故事情节。<br></li><li>通过提比的眼睛看世界，解开关于你自己和一个失落已久文明的谜团。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/b9c5d6203677d41426a598f73e905544.poster.avif?t=1667488910\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/b9c5d6203677d41426a598f73e905544.webm?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1162280/extras/b9c5d6203677d41426a598f73e905544.mp4?t=1667488910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
